{"tid":2260398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【青山派發現】女子拒戴口罩兼吐口水，遭勇武男乘客怒推落車","createTime":"2020-10-27T14:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T14:06:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb52a7bd1da574f827d1c9f2ac5697482ab15a4","tid":2260398,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q9MhRF93WfC3TBbts6mYMQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/4cf2a160-1828-11eb-bf94-e190b0be9425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq9MhRF93WfC3TBbts6mYMQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F4cf2a160-1828-11eb-bf94-e190b0be9425&h=c781787c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大溫哥華交通運輸系統「TransLink」今年8月已實施強制口罩令，要求除了5歲以下小童或有醫療需要人士外，所有乘客須戴口罩。惟近日網上瘋傳一段短片，片中女子不但拒戴口罩，更向勸籲男子吐口水，最終遭對方怒推下車。<br />\n<br />\n片段拍攝日子未明，疑事發於喜士定東街一間日本餐廳外的巴士站，由一名巴士乘客拍到。長30秒影片可見，一名戴太陽眼鏡的女子沒戴口罩就登上巴士，引來在座一名男乘客不滿及指摘其行為「惡心」，女子隨即怒沖沖向他吐口水。<br />\n<br />\n男子憤怒地站起及將女子推向門邊，恰好巴士到站打開車門，於是女子狼狽地摔出車外地上。男子其後擦掉臉上口水及返回座位，只有一名女乘客下車扶起女子。警方正調查事件及聯絡拍片的網民，2名當事人都未有報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/新冠肺炎女子拒戴口罩兼吐口水-遭男乘客怒推落車-074516814.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%8B%92%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%85%BC%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4-%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%80%92%E6%8E%A8%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A-074516814.html&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDB5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=0c548145\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/新冠肺炎女子拒戴口罩兼吐口水-遭男乘客怒推落車-074516814.html</a>"},{"pid":"b686c041b755b23eadbe05dfbe192b813f91ebf6","tid":2260398,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"Darwin will prove it"}]}